ed="T" n="0898a29"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0898a29"/><head><date from-iso="+0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16">後唐</date>明州國寧寺<persName key="A008807">𧦬光</persName>傳</head><pb n="0898b" xml:id="T50.2061.0898b" ed="T"/><p><lb
ed="T" n="0898b01"/><persName key="A008807">釋𧦬光</persName>，字<persName key="A008807">登封</persName>，姓吳氏，<placeName key="PL000000012518">永嘉</placeName>人也，唐史官左<lb
ed="T" n="0898b02"/>庶子<persName key="A011669">兢</persName>之裔孫也。幼捨家於陶山寺<!--找不到此地-->剃度。<lb
ed="T" n="0898b03"/>居必介然，不與<anchor xml:id="beg0898003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>常</sic><corr>恒</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0898003"/>人交雜。好自標遇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1953"/>，慢易<lb
ed="T" n="0898b04"/>緇流。多作古調詩，苦僻寡味，得句時有得<lb
ed="T" n="0898b05"/>色。長於草隷，聞<persName key="A013973">陸希聲</persName>謫宦于<placeName key="PL000000018603">豫章</placeName>，<persName key="A008807">光</persName>往<lb
ed="T" n="0898b06"/>謁之。<persName key="A013973">陸</persName>恬靜而傲氣，居于舟中，凡多迴投<lb
ed="T" n="0898b07"/>刺，且不之許接。一日設方計<anchor xml:id="beg0898sgsz6"/>干<anchor xml:id="end0898sgsz6"/>謁，與語數<lb
ed="T" n="0898b08"/>四，苦祈其草法，而授其五指撥鐙訣。<persName key="A008807">光</persName>書<lb
ed="T" n="0898b09"/>體當見酋健，轉腕迴筆，非常所知。乃西上，<lb
ed="T" n="0898b10"/><persName key="A003875">昭宗</persName>詔對御榻前書，賜紫方袍。後謁<placeName key="PL000000043315">華</placeName>帥<lb
ed="T" n="0898b11"/><persName key="A013974">韓建</persName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0898004"/>薦<anchor xml:id="end0898004"/>號曰<persName key="A008807">廣利</persName>。自<placeName key="PL000000043315">華下</placeName>歸<placeName key="PL000000012518">故鄉</placeName>，謁<persName key="A003552">武肅<lb
ed="T" n="0898b12"/>王錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>，以客禮延之。而性畔岸，弗愜王情，<lb
ed="T" n="0898b13"/>乃歸<placeName key="PL000000013798">甬東</placeName>終焉。有文集，知音者所貴。出筆<lb
ed="T" n="0898b14"/>法弟子<persName key="A013976">從瓌</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000012520">溫州</placeName>僧正<persName key="A013975">智琮</persName>，皆得墨訣。有<lb
ed="T" n="0898b15"/>朝賢贈歌詩，<persName key="A013963">吳內翰融</persName>、<persName key="A009976">羅江東隱</persName>等五十家，<lb
ed="T" n="0898b16"/>僅成一集。時<placeName key="PL000000012470">四明</placeName>太守<persName key="A013977">仰詮</persName>素重<persName key="A008807">光</persName>高蹈，躬<lb
ed="T" n="0898b17"/>為喪主，理命令葬。後三年，准西域焚之，發<lb
ed="T" n="0898b18"/>棺儼若生相，髭髮爪皆長。茶毘收舍利，起<lb
ed="T" n="0898b19"/>小塔焉，則<date key="j20608222062184" notAfter-iso="+0933-12-19" notBefore-iso="+0930-03-28">後唐<name>長興</name>中</date>也。</p>
